    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/3329f5de41e4d29de100282b086a6afb.avif?t=1769707911\" width=800 height=288 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Action and rhythm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a unique universe blending rhythm and combat! Earn attack points by playing with the tempo, optimize your dodges, strike, and launch enemies into the air to chain combos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/543d18c50fb9d6a61cb92dbdcb990a27.poster.avif?t=1769707911\" width=640 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/543d18c50fb9d6a61cb92dbdcb990a27.webm?t=1769707911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/543d18c50fb9d6a61cb92dbdcb990a27.mp4?t=1769707911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets of the primordial planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your combat style as you like, or adjust the difficulty through various game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a classic mode filled with biomes and bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a Boss Rush mode for the daring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a relaxed mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/2844cc8f59a70209f7a7ee368a08d315.poster.avif?t=1769707911\" width=640 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/2844cc8f59a70209f7a7ee368a08d315.webm?t=1769707911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/2844cc8f59a70209f7a7ee368a08d315.mp4?t=1769707911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo lets you explore the first level and its boss, fight part of the bestiary, and try out the level 1 skill tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras/bc352fdca904a0aa1d91ba1964ec3adc.avif?t=1769707911\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219690/extras_big/bc352fdca904a0aa1d91ba1964ec3adc.avif?t=1769707911 width=800 height=144 /></span></p>",
